                        <interp inst="t18390617-name-282" type="surname" value="JONES"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18390617-name-282" type="given" value="LEONARD"></interp>LEONARD JONES</persName>
                  </hi>. These spades are mine—I left them safe on the 22nd of May, and hid them behind the canvas, at the back of the summer-house—the prisoner had no right there—I do not know him.</p>
